intro: This champion of justice has crushed countless evils via the purity of his heart. He used to be a normal boy who just loved superheroes...a lot.

post.body: hey humans! I'm happy to be here! I'm on a directive from Yo-Kai World City Hall to experiment with new ways to communicate with humans. Doesn't mean I'm not friendly. Because I am! :)
@Peeper: Your zite isn't loading properly for me. :(

comment.body: @Homegrown: I do but my arms are kind of stubby so I have to make do with what I have. Plus my new powers help a lot too.
@styromaniac@zeroid.bit: I'm not related to batman. He's alive, I'm not.
